<section id="CancelingAService" role="topic">
    <title id="CancelingAService.title">How to Cancel Your Registration to &ServiceName;</title>
    <para>You can cancel your registration with &ServiceName; at any time.</para>
    <orderedlist>
        <title>To cancel your registration with &ServiceName;</title>
        <listitem>
            <para>Go to <ulink url="http://aws.amazon.com">aws.amazon.com</ulink></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Point to <guilabel>Your Account</guilabel> and click <guilabel>Account
                    Activity</guilabel>.</para>
            <para>The <guilabel>Account Activity</guilabel> page displays.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Click the <guilabel>View/Edit Service</guilabel> link under &ServiceName;.</para>
            <para>The <guilabel>View/Edit Service </guilabel>page displays.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Click the link, <guilabel>cancel this service</guilabel>. </para>
            <simpara>This link is typically in the last sentence of the opening paragraph.</simpara>
        </listitem>
    </orderedlist>
</section>
